</picture></div></div><div
class="block-intro-text"><p>Small businesses are the heartbeat of the American economy. What starts as a simple idea from a motivated entrepreneur can become a thriving business that attracts hundreds if not thousands of customers and keeps dozens of people employed.</p></div></div></div></div><div
class="section-content"><div
class="container"><div
class="narrow-container"><div
class="block"><p>Every business idea needs to be researched, planned, financed, registered, insured, and promoted before it becomes a reality. If you can work through each of the appropriate steps without cutting corners, you can emerge with a profitable business that you can be proud of.</p></div><div
class="block block-download"><div
class="download-wrapper"><div
